text: Goera is a genus of caddisflies in the family Goeridae. There are at least 120 described species in Goera. The type species for Goera is Phryganea pilosa J.C. Fabricius. ==See also== * List of Goera species ==References== ==Further reading== * * * * Category:Trichoptera genera Category:Integripalpia
title: Goera
